snippet.title: Sonic Robo Blast 2 v2.2 - 20th Anniversary Trailer
snippet.description:
Sonic Robo Blast 2 started in March 1998 as a Klik-N-Play game before moving to the DooM engine, and is still alive and kicking with a large, thriving community. The game remains in active development, and to celebrate the anniversary of its genesis we've made this trailer to show you a little bit of what's next. While the content of this video is currently up to date, things can and will change before release.

While you wait, why not head to http://www.srb2.org/ and check out version 2.1?
